snippet.textDisplay:
Wish it was easier to just say Goodbye… 
But in hindsight with and every song, someone creates their own memories filled with each new every emotion filling every void. Somewhere down the line this season’s song gonna play and air linger on our face and remind us how Zulfi ji created history with every song and we filled the void by listening around the world. 
In India 🇮🇳 we have double the fun by experiencing with @JyotiSardar , discussing the production, experiencing the magical journey together, it’s so heart warming and her reactions n analysis are priceless 🤌🏻 
It’s not a goodbye…
It’s a see you next time… until then🩵
